text: Aditya Jagtap (born 7 May 1992) is an Indian male squash player. He is currently competing at the 2019-20 PSA World Tour. He achieved his highest career ranking of 77 in September 2019. Aditya is currently ranked 77 according to the world rankings. Jagtap graduated from Cornell University in 2015 while playing on the Big Red men's squash team. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Indian male squash players Category:Cornell Big Red men's squash players Category:People from Ahmednagar
